node.text:
YUP!!! @callouts is a BRAND NEW matchmaking platform that just launched! This app makes it SO easy to find that special someone with the same interests as you in the fitness world. It’s hard to go out and meet people who understand the fitness lifestyle.. Now, it’s easier than ever. Whether you’re looking for a boyfriend/girlfriend, make a new friend or lifting partner, @callouts is the perfect app to match you to that special someone! Are you a powerlifter, bodybuilder, crossfitter or someone who just enjoys living a healthy lifestyle? Now, you can find someone who has the same interests and it’s all right on your phone. It takes 2 minutes to create a profile! After your profile is created, you can start browsing and chatting with members. SO exciting! Everyone go and download @callouts on the App Store right now

#dating #fitness #callouts #itsnotforthemitsforus #gymfam #ad
